To build and install lgmon:

        for rpm
        ./autogen.sh --program-suffix=<Printer Model Name>
        for deb
        ./autogen.sh --prefix=/usr --enable-progpath=/usr/bin --program-suffix=<Printer Model Name>
        make
        make install

To build and install lgmon with AUTOCONF

You can set the following <Printer Model Name>.
            ip100
            mx890
            mx710
            mx510
            mx430
            mx370
            e600

Example for building the mx890 lgmon with the new automake and autoconf:
        for rpm
        ./autogen.sh --program-suffix=mx890
        for deb
        ./autogen.sh --prefix=/usr --enable-progpath=/usr/bin --program-suffix=mx890
        make
        make install

